Former Australia cricket captain
Ricky Ponting agreed to play for Surrey for two months later
this year, the English cricket club said on its website.  Ponting, 38, will play for the team in June and July as
cover for Surrey captain Graeme Smith who will be on
international duty for South Africa, the website said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
